{"word":"Dibon","slug":"dibon","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Dibon</b> <a href=\"#/H1769\">H1769</a> <br/> 1. Called Dibongad and Dimon<br/> - A city on the northern banks of the Arnon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=21&verse=30'>Num 21:30</a> <br/> - Israelites encamp at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=33&verse=45'>Num 33:45</a> <br/> - Allotted to Gad and Reuben<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=3'>Num 32:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=34'>Num 32:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=9'>Jos 13:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=17'>Jos 13:17</a> <br/> - Taken by Moab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=15&verse=2'>Isa 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=15&verse=9'>Isa 15:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=18'>Jer 48:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=22'>Jer 48:22</a> <br/> 2. A city in the tribe of Judah<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=25'>Neh 11:25</a> <br/> - Probably identical with Dimonah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=22'>Jos 15:22</a> "}]}